text: Jitendra Kumar Gothwal is an Indian politician and current Member of the Rajasthan Legislative Assembly from Khandar Sawai Madhopur in Rajasthan. He is a Bharatiya Janata Party politician.Jitendra Kumar Gothwal MLA bio profile ==References== Category:Rajasthani politicians Category:Living people Category:1973 births
